{"type":"user.message","data":{"content":"I have a NativeAOT .NET 11 app running in Kubernetes. The createdump\ntool is installed at /opt/tools/createdump. Configure automatic crash\ndump collection and give me the pod spec changes I need.\n","transformedContent":"<current_datetime>2026-04-04T00:55:53.490Z</current_datetime>\n\nI have a NativeAOT .NET 11 app running in Kubernetes. The createdump\ntool is installed at /opt/tools/createdump. Configure automatic crash\ndump collection and give me the pod spec changes I need.","attachments":[],"interactionId":"9ffc02ee-4da6-4ed5-a658-671347d47f5b"},"id":"593ed1bc-bc40-41a6-a7ce-11d98f07e49c","timestamp":"2026-04-04T00:55:53.490Z","parentId":"bdf98b04-8160-41fc-937a-447e394fdb38"}
